Medicare Temporal Endpoint

Source: R/S7_care.R
care_temporal.Rd

Medicare Temporal Endpoint

Usage

care_temporal(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> title alias

Value

An S7 <care_temporal> object.

Examples

care_temporal("quality_payment")
